President's Press Secy Ashok Malik resigns from ITC board.
New Delhi, Aug 1 (PTI) Diversified conglomerate ITC today said Ashok Malik, who has been appointed the press secretary of the President of India, has resigned from its board of directors. "Ashok Malik resigned from the board of directors of the company with effect from close of work on July 31, 2017, consequent on his appointment as press secretary to the President of India," the company said. 